hyperrealistic, a girl sings a song

You can use either context options, or the original long gen method.

When using context options, set num_frames and frame_window_size to be equal'

Otherwise set frame_window_size to something the model is capbable of doing normally, original default is 77, 81 seems to work too.

Original method is probably better for motion etc, and is faster, but the benefit of context windows is that it doesn't degrade over time on long clips.
